Description:
Order Instituting Rulemaking Pursuant to Senate Bill No. 790 to Consider and Adopt a Code of Conduct, Rules and Enforcement Procedures Governing the Conduct of Electrical Corporations Relative to the Consideration, Formation and Implementation of Community Choice Aggregation Programs.

Opening Comments on the Proposed Rules are due by March 26, 2012;
Reply Comments on the Proposed Rules are due by April 16, 2012;
Motions for Hearing are due by April 23. 2012;
Responses to Motions for Hearing are due by April 30. 2012.
